  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6358276/" class="title-link">不是所有人都有资格谈复仇</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6358276"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/49499467/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u49499467-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/49499467/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">才云鹏</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-10-28"
      class="main-meta">2013-10-28 09:38:48</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6358276_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  才云鹏 2013年10月24日《杭州日报》http://hzdaily.hangzhou.com.cn/hzrb/html/2013-10/24/content_1601557.htm  我的家乡吉林省松原市，于2012年建起了世界最高的成吉思汗雕塑，舆论立刻对此褒贬不一。雕塑之建立，缘于松原市下辖某县是蒙古族自治县，蒙古人对其久远领袖的膜...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/6358276/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 3没用</span>
                  </div>
